    <span class="post-cat">Software Review · AI Content + SEO</span>
    <h1>Scalenut Review 2026: Cruise Mode Tested — Honest Verdict</h1>
    <p class="description">Scalenut bundles SEO research, briefs, AI drafting, and content scoring into one tool — and Cruise Mode genuinely produces usable first drafts in five minutes. It also <strong>still leaves you with editing, fact-checking, and publishing to handle</strong>. After 30 days of side-by-side testing against Surfer + Jasper, here is the honest 2026 verdict.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
